 ring setting! Begin by sketching directly from artwork in the collection 
 to sharpen your eye and strengthen your skills. Then\, move into the stud
 io to learn about color theory and add color to your artwork.</p><ul><li>
 Strengthen fundamental drawing skills  </li><li>Explore color theory in a
 ction  </li><li>Experiment with color media  </li><li>Expand your creativ
 e expression in a hands-on way  </li></ul><p><span data-contrast="auto">R
 eserve your spot. If this page says\, "Registration has closed" that mean
 s the waitlist is full.</span></p><h3><strong>Supplies</strong></h3><ul><
